      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one pot</strong> <strong>creamy chicken thigh florentine</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>torn basil </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
